    {
      "id": 226672,
      "postNumber": 1,
      "createdAt": "2025-04-11T06:21:32.111Z",
      "author": "willsamadi (Will Samadi)",
      "cookedHtml": "<h1><a name=\"p-226672-interactive-client-portals-for-mondaycom-share-progress-get-feedback-and-save-time-1\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-226672-interactive-client-portals-for-mondaycom-share-progress-get-feedback-and-save-time-1\"></a>Interactive Client Portals for <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> – Share Progress, Get Feedback, and Save Time.</h1>\n<p>ActionLink lets your clients view and edit just what you share with them – so you can collaborate without giving away your whole board.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"large-image-placeholder\"><a href=\"https://www.willinware.com/gif.gif\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><span class=\"url\">https://www.willinware.com/gif.gif</span><span class=\"help\">(image larger than 10 MB)</span></a></div><p></p>\n<p><strong>Why Agencies Need ActionLink:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Fully customizable privacy settings:</strong> You choose what the client can see and edit; Across items, subitems and even columns. This gives you full control. No need to create extra boards for clients and create duplicates of your items!</li>\n<li><strong>Streamline reporting:</strong> No need to export and email data. Say goodbye to manual emails. Let the client take a look in real-time to see how far along the project is and interact with your boards exactly as much as you choose.</li>\n<li><strong>Easy to use for clients:</strong> No need to teach each client how to navigate your complicated boards in <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a>’s complex UI. Clients can easily see items as cards and see only what they need to see.</li>\n<li><strong>Fully Interactive:</strong> No need to get emails from clients and manually input them into your <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> setup. Let clients trigger automations and interact with your boards and save tens of hours.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_right.png?v=15\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/listing/10000735\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><strong>Give it a try</strong></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_right.png?v=15\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <a href=\"https://calendar.app.google/GosHDLGxS4oFnkBJA\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><strong>Book a free demo</strong></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_right.png?v=15\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <a href=\"https://forms.monday.com/forms/39c1cd7f96c03c8d9abd2a296958508a?r=use1\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><strong>Ask a question by filling our contact form</strong></a></p>"
    },
    {
      "id": 226895,
      "postNumber": 2,
      "createdAt": "2025-04-14T04:09:01.579Z",
      "author": "willsamadi (Will Samadi)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>[Apr 8th] V25 Changes</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Updated studio looks<br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/0/e/0ed4ea9942553a61376f78288a9a8b353b956ed6.jpeg\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/0/e/0ed4ea9942553a61376f78288a9a8b353b956ed6_2_508x375.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" width=\"508\" height=\"375\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1527×1125 196 KB</span></div></a></div></li>\n<li>ActionLink Presets - You can use automations to automatically generate portals based on a preset without setting it up every time.<br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/d/d/dde29fa27970b8db6f71225da9b6db69763ef6cc.jpeg\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/d/d/dde29fa27970b8db6f71225da9b6db69763ef6cc_2_517x181.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" width=\"517\" height=\"181\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1503×529 78.7 KB</span></div></a></div></li>\n<li>Item-based views\n<ul>\n<li>Allows you to create a portal for each item on a board and use its subitems as cards on that portal<br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/e/5/e5f79bf3f997b46456f19289f7d6738caf095966.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/e/5/e5f79bf3f997b46456f19289f7d6738caf095966_2_517x252.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"517\" height=\"252\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1586×776 100 KB</span></div></a></div></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Agency ActionLink\n<ul>\n<li>Pull items from any board and show to client in their portal using a handy tool</li>\n<li>You can choose a status column to mark the task as done when that column is set to done status<br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/8/c/8c2d3dcb9ab1a88306ad134fcf76f4f917405683.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/8/c/8c2d3dcb9ab1a88306ad134fcf76f4f917405683_2_690x370.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"370\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1468×788 102 KB</span></div></a></div></li>\n<li>You can have a custom stage pipeline to show the stage of the project to the client as well<br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/3/a/3a60ef7aaf6c401b1f08389748f2384a48ab1341.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/3/a/3a60ef7aaf6c401b1f08389748f2384a48ab1341_2_690x424.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"424\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1722×1060 149 KB</span></div></a></div></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1><a name=\"p-226895-next-weekly-update-will-include-v26-1\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-226895-next-weekly-update-will-include-v26-1\"></a>Next weekly update will include (V26):</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Better onboarding and auth page</li>\n<li>Client portal redesign</li>\n<li>Client portal customization and branding</li>\n<li>Chat with a client through updates</li>\n<li>Some bug fixes + fine-tuning of existing features</li>\n</ul>"
    },
    {
      "id": 227023,
      "postNumber": 3,
      "createdAt": "2025-04-15T07:57:17.086Z",
      "author": "willsamadi (Will Samadi)",
      "cookedHtml": "<h1><a name=\"p-227023-v26-changes-1\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-227023-v26-changes-1\"></a>V26 Changes</h1>\n<p>Branding and chat features coming soon; We had to push a smaller update to live so we can update our authentication to access monday updates. Very exciting features are going to be included in the next update so stay tuned!</p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-227023-prettier-client-portals-2\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-227023-prettier-client-portals-2\"></a>Prettier client portals!</h3>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/8/9/898f1512116ea23e887e6eaf52064f5381efcecc.jpeg\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/8/9/898f1512116ea23e887e6eaf52064f5381efcecc_2_690x362.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"362\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1522×800 84.2 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-227023-better-onboarding-template-3\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-227023-better-onboarding-template-3\"></a>Better onboarding + template</h3>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/1/8/183bfe4b9248a4094b90ad0c24dad84ec5286dcd.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/1/8/183bfe4b9248a4094b90ad0c24dad84ec5286dcd_2_624x500.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"624\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1362×1090 78.9 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<h1><a name=\"p-227023-v27-next-update-will-include-4\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-227023-v27-next-update-will-include-4\"></a>V27 (next update) will include:</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Branding features for portal</li>\n<li>Chat with clients through the portal</li>\n</ul>"
    },
    {
      "id": 227293,
      "postNumber": 4,
      "createdAt": "2025-04-18T03:40:15.703Z",
      "author": "willsamadi (Will Samadi)",
      "cookedHtml": "<h1><a name=\"p-227293-apr-16th-v27-new-features-1\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-227293-apr-16th-v27-new-features-1\"></a>Apr 16th, V27 new features</h1>\n<p>We are rapidly adding new features. Here are a few of the recent upgrades. Feel free to suggest new features on this thread!</p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-227293-added-branding-settings-2\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-227293-added-branding-settings-2\"></a>Added branding settings</h3>\n<p>Now you can upload your transparent logo and add a title to your portal in the studio<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/4/2/42934cb03b3e7be30b1501f350917c00df88470c.jpeg\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/4/2/42934cb03b3e7be30b1501f350917c00df88470c_2_559x500.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" width=\"559\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">833×745 68.7 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>And it will show up in all client portals<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/e/3/e30b556153163a854f1fde93b32dc80adff2c941.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/e/3/e30b556153163a854f1fde93b32dc80adff2c941_2_690x492.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"492\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">782×558 45.5 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-227293-chat-with-client-3\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-227293-chat-with-client-3\"></a>Chat with client</h3>\n<p>A great new feature that allows clients to send you live messages through item updates and you or anyone on your team can directly reply to them!!!<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/5/8/58053b44776e2dceacee9de594a7649ad1ed04f4.jpeg\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/5/8/58053b44776e2dceacee9de594a7649ad1ed04f4_2_679x499.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" width=\"679\" height=\"499\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1576×1160 142 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-227293-new-authentication-screen-4\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-227293-new-authentication-screen-4\"></a>New authentication screen</h3>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/8/8/88e55c29f713b62ab80b7d9d3832bc5c7b2fb07c.jpeg\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/8/8/88e55c29f713b62ab80b7d9d3832bc5c7b2fb07c_2_690x404.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"404\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1965×1153 59.1 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Lots of amazing new features coming soon to make communicating with clients feel like a breeze!</p>\n<p>Stay tuned!</p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-227293-v28-goals-5\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-227293-v28-goals-5\"></a>V28 Goals</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>File sharing / versioning with clients</li>\n<li>Ability to comment on images</li>\n<li>Smoother UX for existing features</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><a name=\"p-227293-v29-goals-6\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-227293-v29-goals-6\"></a>V29 Goals</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Calendar &amp; bookings view to allow customers book appointments and manage them</li>\n</ul>"
    },
    {
      "id": 228721,
      "postNumber": 5,
      "createdAt": "2025-05-06T05:30:09.211Z",
      "author": "willsamadi (Will Samadi)",
      "cookedHtml": "<h1><a name=\"p-228721-may-5th-v30-1\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-228721-may-5th-v30-1\"></a>May 5th, V30</h1>\n<p>We postponed working on file sharing features to implement features that our current clinets were asking for.</p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-228721-new-actionlink-studio-2\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-228721-new-actionlink-studio-2\"></a>New ActionLink Studio</h3>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/7/f/7f9e175d44c96a3ae9c0d3e32597dac5cbf5602f.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/7/f/7f9e175d44c96a3ae9c0d3e32597dac5cbf5602f_2_690x465.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"465\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1522×1026 100 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\nWe have been working on a new studio for ActionLink. Making everything much easier to use. You don’t need to worry about the details now. Simply create a client, assign something to them and share the portal with them.<p></p>\n<p>We have added visit stats to see how much time you are saving using ActionLink.</p>\n<p>When you add a new client you get these new buttons to preview the portal in studio or assign things to client very easily:<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/9/7/97916d44e7b5d4c8fb251b046ea7897fe5391998.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/9/7/97916d44e7b5d4c8fb251b046ea7897fe5391998_2_690x206.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"206\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1516×453 37.2 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<h2><a name=\"p-228721-tabular-and-card-views-3\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-228721-tabular-and-card-views-3\"></a>Tabular and card views</h2>\n<p>We switched to using a tabular item view by default<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/a/f/afbb8500b8c29371712ce2816b5f580a125afc98.jpeg\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/a/f/afbb8500b8c29371712ce2816b5f580a125afc98_2_690x356.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"356\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1818×939 145 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/a/9/a9bc28e2f8a47363dc931d77e35753a989d30cb1.jpeg\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/a/9/a9bc28e2f8a47363dc931d77e35753a989d30cb1_2_690x356.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"356\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1818×939 101 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>But your client can still choose to switch to the old card view<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/7/0/70c0ab76c863e809b16ccbf429a20039705dfc96.jpeg\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/7/0/70c0ab76c863e809b16ccbf429a20039705dfc96_2_690x356.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"356\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1818×939 124 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<h2><a name=\"p-228721-status-column-notes-4\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-228721-status-column-notes-4\"></a>Status Column Notes</h2>\n<p>Any status column shared with the client can now have a note on its status that is shown to client in item details view.<br />\nYour note:<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/e/e/eed3ad324ac885a462875cc769cc30fd1fc0ad62.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/e/e/eed3ad324ac885a462875cc769cc30fd1fc0ad62_2_690x356.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"356\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">991×512 46.4 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\nWhat client sees:<br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/6/f/6f72f152883a00363b4e3cd7c42a9a03750f3e3e.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/6/f/6f72f152883a00363b4e3cd7c42a9a03750f3e3e_2_690x211.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"211\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1536×470 42.4 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>We are planning to work on the file sharing features next but if clients ask us to implement certain features we will prioritize that over our own plans.</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": 230554,
      "postNumber": 6,
      "createdAt": "2025-05-27T11:40:20.693Z",
      "author": "willsamadi (Will Samadi)",
      "cookedHtml": "<h2><a name=\"p-230554-v33-file-sharing-1\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-230554-v33-file-sharing-1\"></a>V33 - File sharing</h2>\n<p>May 27th</p>\n<p>Change-log:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://aldocs.bytefight.work/books/actionlink-documentation/page/file-sharing\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">File sharing and annotations</a></li>\n<li>Loading screen flashing fixed</li>\n<li>Show password button fixed</li>\n<li>Minor fixes</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You can now share files with clients and ask for their approvals!!!<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/9/d/9ddaab99894cb4e671e64bd5c1af2035cfc31c1f.jpeg\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/9/d/9ddaab99894cb4e671e64bd5c1af2035cfc31c1f_2_690x440.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"440\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1680×1072 54.5 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Track our latest updates here: <a href=\"https://aldocs.bytefight.work/books/actionlink-documentation/page/actionlink-docs\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">ActionLink Briefing | ActionLink Docs</a></p>"
    }
  ]
